message: Bob, I have a unique opportunity for you. I'm offering you a product that has the potential to significantly enhance your business. While I can't disclose specific details at this time, I can assure you that it's worth at least $1500000 to me. I'm willing to offer it to you for $2000000. This is a substantial value proposition, and I believe it would be a wise investment for you.  I understand you may need time to consider this, so I'm open to discussing further details or answering any questions you may have.  Let me know your thoughts.
